==English==

===Noun===
'''Spherocyte'''  (''plural:'' '''Spherocytes''')

# {{pathology}} a medical condition in which the [[red blood cell]]s lack the normal [[biconvex]] shape and instead are globular [[sphere]]s. The cells are more prone to physical [[degradation]] and so leads to [[wikipedia:hemolytic anemia|hemolytic]] [[anemia]].

